HEADWORD: Macrodiagonal
<hw>Mac`ro*di*ag"o*nal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Macro-</ets> + <ets>diagonal</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Crystallog.)</fld> <def>The longer of two diagonals, as of a
rhombic prism. See <er>Crystallization</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

